    Title

    predict_ridge.Rd

    Title

    predict_ridge(obj, newx, cv = TRUE)

    Arguments

    newx

    Examples

    

n <- 100 ; p <- 10
X <- matrix(rnorm(n * p), n, p) # no intercept!
y <- rnorm(n)

fit_obj <- after::fit_ridge(X, y)

n_test <- 10

predict_ridge(fit_obj, newx=matrix(rnorm(n_test * p), n_test, p),
cv=TRUE)

#>  [7] -0.1184286 -0.1184286 -0.1184286 -0.1184286
